item.title: Take Warning! Radio
item.description:
Quite an enjoyable show right here. Stu-Rat and Rawz discuss Paul Gleason, AFI, and more goodness.
The episode ends abruptly and quite eerily. Stu-Rat seems to think we experienced "technical" problems. I believe that God finally subscribed to the podcast and sabotaged our show. Have no fear though, God did email and we are all cool now.
Take Warning Radio: takewarning@comcast.net www.myspace.com/takewarningradio ~Rawz

item.title: Aces Wild part 2
item.description:
Here is the second episode (of three) of Take Warning Radio's "Aces Wild" show featuring Rawz, Stu-Rat, and Andy. For those of you who have asked, "what is that hissing sound in the background during this show?" The answer- that's my girlfriend steam cleaning in the background. Now THAT'S punk rock! Right?...yeah....it's not...
For those of you who use iTunes to get this podcast, check out the link below for our "enhanced" podcast (be sure to have your album art window open while checking it out)
Until next time.
~take warning radio
